		<img alt="" height="254" src="images/horse_pic_3.jpg" width="380" class="style2" />
		<h2 class="style1" style="height: 25px"> Relationship First</h2>
		<p>Our mission is to build a relationship based on trust with our horses.  
		This relationship is created from the heart, NOT the mind. 
		The goal is to connect with our horses by using a shared language which allows us a greater understanding of both the horses and ourselves. 
		</p>
		<p>We teach and work with the horses in an environment that appreciates the intelligence of these amazing animals.  
		Our focus is based on Trust, Respect and Safety and therefore no longer aligned with methods of obedience, submissiveness and control. 
		By moving away from domination and into a partnership we communicate from the heart which allows for endless possibilities.</p>
